data.description: Welcome to Colorado Ave, a stunning property located in the highly sought-after Lincoln Park area. Situated on an expansive nearly half-acre lot with perfect garden area, this home is a nature lover's paradise. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, this spacious residence offers ample room for comfortable living. The newly remodeled kitchen offers custom countertops & island. Experience the perfect blend of functionality, and relaxation in this remarkable main suite. From walk-in closets to the newly remodeled bath with his and her sinks, every detail has been carefully curated to elevate your living experience. Unwind, rejuvenate, and enjoy the peaceful moments in your private sanctuary. Adjacent to the main suite, you'll find a delightful sitting area that offers a serene escape. Start your day right by stepping out onto the deck, immersing yourself in the tranquil surroundings. Savor a cup of coffee as you breathe in the fresh air. For car enthusiasts and hobbyists, the property features a detached oversized 2-car garage measuring an impressive 24 x 36, providing plenty of room for vehicles and additional storage. Additionally, there are two large sheds, offering even more space for tools, equipment, or recreational items. As an added bonus, new Anderson Low E windows will be installed, enhancing energy efficiency and providing an abundance of natural light. A new roof and skylight are soon to be installed, ensuring peace of mind and adding to the home's aesthetic appeal.
